divs: Sighting DetailsI was at a concert with some friends a long time ago and i took a picture of a friends face without him knowing, like a oke. but when i looked at the picture i saw something in the background. The first thing i thought was it was a UFO, because im into all that stuff, and conspiracies, things like that. And my friend said it was probably a bug and i said no, because it was too high up and far away, it looks more like an object, or something flying, it also reminded me of those dementors from harry potter. Soo i dont know anything about it, i have seen UFOs with my eyes recently and also in the ast but i have never caught one on camera on accident.
Summary: I was at a concert with friends. took a picture of friends face as joke. Found something in background.
